{
"#useparam"
:
true
,
"#name"
:
{
"x qywx"
:
null
,
"cn"
:
"使用企业微信群机器人发送消息"
,
"en"
:
"Send messages using a WXwork group bot"
}
,
"#desc"
:
{
"cn"
:
"使用 x qywx 向你的企业微信群发送消息。首次使用需要配置 webhook url。"
,
"en"
:
"Use x qywx send messages to your WXwork group. The first use requires configuring webhook url."
}
,
"#tip"
:
[
{
"en"
:
"Instructions for get the webhook url for WXwork group bot:  https://developer.work.weixin.qq.com/document/path/91770\n- Interactive env use `x qywx init` to initialize configuration. The configure will be saved locally.\n- Run command `x qywx --cfg webhook=<webhook_url>` to add webhook url.\n"
,
"cn"
:
"企业微信群机器人 webhook url 获取指引: https://developer.work.weixin.qq.com/document/path/91770\n- 交互环境中可使用 `x qywx init` 进行初始化配置，配置信息将存放于本地保存\n- 亦可运行命令 `x qywx --cfg webhook=<webhook_url>` 添加 webhook url\n"
}
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x qywx --cfg webhook=<webhook>"
,
"cn"
:
"设置 webhook url"
,
"en"
:
"set webhook url"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x qywx send --text \"x-cmd 新版本发布成功\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送文本消息到企业微信群"
,
"en"
:
"Send text type messages to WXwork group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x qywx send --markdown \"## x-cmd 新版本发布成功\\n v1.0.0\""
,
"cn"
:
"发送 markdown 消息到企业微信群"
,
"en"
:
"Send markdown type messages to your WXwork group"
}
,
{
"cmd"
:
"x qywx send --image ./test.png"
,
"cn"
:
"发送图片 \"test.png\" 到企业微信群"
,
"en"
:
"Send local image to your WXwork group"
}
]
,
"#subcmd:config"
:
[
"init"
,
"--cfg"
,
"--cur"
]
,
